            "Adjusted": "No change"
        },
        {
            "Original": "The client places the identifier of the server that allocated the lease(s) in a Server Identifier option (seeSection 21.3).",
            "Adjusted": "The client places the identifier of the server that allocated the lease(s) in a Server Identifier option (see Section 21.3)."
