            "Original": "The client transmits the message according to Section 15, using the following parameters: IRT REL_TIMEOUT MRT 0 MRC REL_MAX_RC MRD 0 If leases are released but the Reply from a DHCP server is lost, the client will retransmit the Release message, and the server may respond with a Reply indicating a status of NoBinding.",
            "Adjusted": "The client transmits the message according to Section 15, using the following parameters: IRT REL_TIMEOUT, MRT 0, MRC REL_MAX_RC, MRD 0. If leases are released but the Reply from a DHCP server is lost, the client will retransmit the Release message, and the server may respond with a Reply indicating a status of NoBinding."
