            "Adjusted": "The client transmits the message according to Section 15, using the following parameters: IRT REN_TIMEOUT, MRT REN_MAX_RT, MRC 0, MRD remaining time until earliest T2. The message exchange is terminated when the earliest time T2 is reached."
        },
        {
            "Original": "While the client is responding to a Reconfigure, the client ignores and discards any additional Reconfigure messages it may receive.",
