            "Adjusted": "No change"
        },
        {
            "Original": "The server ignores addresses not assigned to the IAs (though it may choose to log an error if it finds such addresses).",
            "Adjusted": "The server ignores addresses not assigned to the IAs (though the server may choose to log an error if the server finds such addresses)."
