        {
            "Original": "The client includes a Status Code option (see Section 21.13) with the value Success, a Server Identifier option (see Section 21.3) with the server's DUID, and a Client Identifier option (see Section 21.2) with the client's DUID.",
            "Adjusted": "The server includes a Status Code option (see Section 21.13) with the value Success, a Server Identifier option (see Section 21.3) with the server's DUID, and a Client Identifier option (see Section 21.2) with the client's DUID."
