            "Original": "There may, however, be reasons for having a very long refresh time, so it may be useful for this maximum value to be configurable.",
            "Adjusted": "There may, however, be reasons for having a very long refresh time, so it may be useful for the maximum refresh time value to be configurable."
        }
    ]
